      "writtenOn": "2020-03-25T20:16:17Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Just throwing the question out there, but is there a better pattern that this? I\u0027ve never really liked it in Vulkan. Basically we pass in the GrVkRT into the GrVkCB call, and then we call back the GrVkRT passing in the GrVkCB to add resources to. Would it be cleaner if this just returned a list of resources or maybe better you explicitly asked for the resources that need to be reffed? Like getColorTargetMangedResource() (would return either msaa or non msaa whatever is the actually rendering target), getSteniclMangedResource(), etc.?",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 54,
        "startChar": 4,
        "endLine": 54,
        "endChar": 53
      },
      "revId": "6cfaa5b84bdb96181c9686301ce45bc08135bb82",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": true
    },
